@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using WebTinTuc.Data.Entities
@inject SignInManager<User> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<User> UserManager

<ul class="navbar-nav">
    @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-white" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Manage/Index">Xin chào, @((await UserManager.GetUserAsync(User))?.FullName ?? User.Identity?.Name)!</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <form class="form-inline" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Logout" asp-route-returnUrl="@Url.Action("Index", "Home", new { area = "" })">
                <button type="submit" class="nav-link btn btn-link text-white border-0">Đăng xuất</button>
            </form>
        </li>
    }
    else
    {
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link text-white" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Register">Đăng ký</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link text-white" asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Login">Đăng nhập</a></li>
    }
</ul>